EN: She crazily scratched her arm.

ZH: 他的眼镜擦伤了，所以他看不清楚。
EN: His glasses got scratched, so he can't see clearly.

ZH: 他的背部因为撞击而出现了擦伤。
EN: He has a scrape on his back from the impact.

ZH: 小孩子们擦伤了膝盖，哭了起来。
EN: The children scraped their knees and started crying.

ZH: 坐地上擦伤了屁股，感觉很痛。
EN: I scraped my butt sitting on the ground, it hurts.

ZH: 他的皮鞋擦伤了，现在看起来不再光亮。
EN: He has scratched his leather shoes, now they don't look shiny anymore.
